on=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1448\" data-rawheight=\"634\" data-original-token=\"v2-87b04f7e0bfd7eefd0070034b144e5e0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-86a427532c7709dd615b63ea2cbc379d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1448\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-87b04f7e0bfd7eefd0070034b144e5e0_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87b04f7e0bfd7eefd0070034b144e5e0_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"dBRnGKYa\">经测试，搜英文和数字一切正常。搜中文就会出现题主的情况，应该是一个 bug，我试试能不能和开发者反馈一下。</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"6h4C1cr9\">更新一下，反馈结果是，中文其实是支持的，但是搜索默认需要输入 3 个及以上的字符。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-original-token=\"v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1ec5212cd682d5cab8c79691973946a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;704&#39; height=&#39;440&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"440\" data-original-token=\"v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1ec5212cd682d5cab8c79691973946a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4205e544ce69093a0321b552455291ad_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"fGo-L1ky\">开发者表示未来会对中文放宽这个标准。</p><p data-pid=\"J0MkMCRQ\">经测试，确实 3 个以上汉字就能搜索了 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7646dd1db8d849b04cabb73372e82518\" data-hash=\"7646dd1db8d849b04cabb73372e82518\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7646dd1db8d849b04cabb73372e82518\">@三石四k</a> </p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1514\" data-rawheight=\"368\" data-original-token=\"v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-88598f72c628a8ef214e68c360f6c443_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1514\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1514&#39; height=&#39;368&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1514\" data-rawheight=\"368\" data-original-token=\"v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-88598f72c628a8ef214e68c360f6c443_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1514\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b59e4b600d618aa66e3672c43b7569f5_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p></p>",
